    • getIndicators

      public static java.util.List<com.github.javaparser.utils.Pair<java.lang.String,​java.lang.String>> getIndicators​(java.lang.String directory, java.lang.String rule, java.lang.String ruleName) throws java.io.IOException
      Open the xlsx file passed in the directory and search in the first line for the column with name equal to rulename, apply the rule to each line of the file and compare the result with the result inserted manually by the user
      Parameters:
      directory - The directory of the file
      rule - The rule
      ruleName - The rule name
      Returns:
      list of pairs String and String, if the rule doesn't exists in the xlsx file return null
      Throws:
      java.io.IOException - Throws IOException if can't read the file
